posts.description: Where'd my warm weather go, Denver? Eating cold treats even on cold days. 😋 This one's straight from my Favorite Things video. Not gonna lie, it's not usually pink. It's more red. I just turn everything pink on Instagram because 💕✨💖✨💕 (code for everything looks better pink).

Happy World Penguin Day! 💖🐧 Throwback to what may be the best day of my life. 😂 For my birthday one year @derekvanschaik arranged for me to meet two penguins: Maddie and Juniper. I was so happy that I cried and Derek said I had to calm down because I would scare the penguins. 😂😍

Inhaling a waffle in the 2 minutes before a morning interview with Buzzfeed. I think it went really well! I'll share the video with you guys when they release it. We talked about princesses and my upcoming music projects. Such a crazy day yesterday I forgot to post this. Set up camera and video equipment, hair and makeup, then the interview started around 8am, then went straight to train a new princess, came back, had 6 Veri chats scheduled with you guys, filmed another video, took care of some business stuff, then went to a 2+ hour Zumba fundraiser. Now I'm off to my dance class. Like why am I typing instead of running out the door? 😂 Good thing I like staying busy. 😅
Side by side or miles apart, we are sisters connected by the ❤. Missing my sisters today. Tag your sister (or a bestie who's like a sister) to share some LOVE. 💖✨

Our hideout room in between performances. The hideaway is honestly way more necessary when I'm singing as a princess than as myself. 😅 Nobody can compete with Elsa when it comes to being mobbed by small children. 😂 + shoutout to @fairytalewigs for giving me this amazing 'do. They styled one too small, and I have a freakishly little head so they sent it to me. 💖

Exploring Vail through rose colored glasses 🌷 My favorite town in all of Colorado. It never gets old. My little slice of Europe in the middle of the US.
Also to all of you who have been to Vail and seen this building in person, you'll know why I said, "Through rose colored glasses..." 😂
We are a family full of blonde girls. 💁🏼 I have a picture in this same spot in Vail with my mom and my other sister... all blondes.
Happy Easter! 🐇💐 Hope your day is filled with flowers, bunnies, and pastel colored eggs!

Afternoon tea at Glen Eyrie Castle has to be one of my favorite things ever. 😍 Appropriate for my new Favorite Things video up on YouTube (link in profile) where I share with you 14 favorite things from bags and hair products to tasty treats and things that just make life easier. My only stipulation was that nothing on the list could be sponsored or given to be by a brand. I just want to share my absolute favorite things in hopes that you'll enjoy them, too. 
Here are some brands that I mention in the video. None of them knew about this, so it's the most genuine recommendation I know how to give. 💖  @musicnotescom @popandsuki @leafandlove @hairstorystudio @themodernpop  @mezzi_official @naturalvitalityofficial @bricsmilano @bumbleandbumble @livingproofinc @riverisland @zevia
Join us for afternoon tea in Glen Eyrie Castle? ✨ Yes please. The weather, the ambience, the food, the company, and everything... just perfect. 😍
